OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRecorded hate crimes treble
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin past decade             
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Recorded hate crimes in England and    
OL,6, Wales have trebled in the past decade, 
OL,7, but fallen by 5% in the last year.     
OL,9,FThe latest figures, which do not       
OL,10,Finclude Devon and Cornwall Police,     
OL,11,Fcover the 12 months to March 2023.     
OL,13,FHowever, religiously motivated hate    
OL,14,Fcrimes and those against transgender   
OL,15,Fpeople have increased.                 
OL,17,FOne expert suggests a change in police 
OL,18,Fguidance on recording incidents could  
OL,19,Fexplain the fall - the first since the 
OL,20,Fdata was first collected in 2013.      
